summary: i feel like dan has 2 reasons to delay the june vid and i believe it’s that it must be something that he‘s anxious about and...
body:
i feel like dan has 2 reasons to delay the june vid and i believe it’s that it must be something that he‘s anxious about and maybe a bit scared to talk about? if it would be a silly vid he wouldn’t be so secretive and closed off about it. i also feel like the tight schedule of the tour adds up to the delay. like yeah it‘s a bummer that we haven’t gotten it yet but i feel like it’s something that is not easy for him as well and he wants to make this right. remember how long he said he took and went back and forth about the depression video.

don’t give him too much shit abt it
